1
00:00:11,041 --> 00:00:13,000
Sir, are you… okay?

2
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:16,625
- Sir? Hey.
- Why is he bleeding?

3
00:00:18,791 --> 00:00:20,916
Sir? Oh… Oh shit.

4
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:22,625
Oh my God. Hey.

5
00:00:46,208 --> 00:00:49,000
<i>Hello, everyone. I'm Witch Baba.</i>

6
00:00:49,083 --> 00:00:51,250
<i>Today is October 5th.</i>

7
00:00:51,333 --> 00:00:55,250
<i>Last time, I predicted</i>
<i>that someone will be stabbed.</i>

8
00:00:55,333 --> 00:00:56,708
<i>And it came true.</i>

9
00:00:56,791 --> 00:00:59,791
<i>Let's see what the tarot cards</i>
<i>have for us today!</i>

10
00:00:59,875 --> 00:01:01,791
<i>Upright Weather Radar.</i>

11
00:01:01,875 --> 00:01:04,083
<i>Reversed London Big Ben.</i>

12
00:01:04,166 --> 00:01:06,208
<i>Reversed Alien.</i>

13
00:01:06,291 --> 00:01:07,750
<i>In the future,</i>

14
00:01:07,833 --> 00:01:10,791
<i>someone will fall to their death</i>
<i>from a bridge.</i>

15
00:01:10,875 --> 00:01:12,375
<i>Yeh Pin-hsuan, take off your mask.</i>

16
00:01:12,458 --> 00:01:14,000
<i>Are the police all sleeping?</i>

17
00:01:14,083 --> 00:01:16,125
<i>What? Can we tag the police to watch this?</i>

18
00:01:16,208 --> 00:01:18,666
- <i>Learn when to stop.</i>
- <i>They fell from a bridge?</i>

19
00:01:18,750 --> 00:01:21,333
- <i>Someone's gonna die again.</i>
- <i>Which bridge? Predict it.</i>

20
00:01:21,416 --> 00:01:23,291
<i>Aren't there</i>
<i>internet police to handle this?</i>

21
00:01:23,375 --> 00:01:25,625
- <i>Witch Baba is Yeh Pin-hsuan?</i>
- <i>Yeh Pin-hsuan.</i>

22
00:01:25,708 --> 00:01:26,708
<i>- Sweet Spot.</i>
<i>- Dox her.</i>

23
00:01:26,791 --> 00:01:28,541
<i>- Murderer!</i>
<i>- Let's make this viral.</i>

24
00:01:28,625 --> 00:01:30,125
WITCH BABA'S IDENTITY EXPOSED!

25
00:01:30,208 --> 00:01:31,666
AN ONLINE CAKE SHOP'S LADY BOSS!

26
00:01:32,375 --> 00:01:33,958
<i>- What the helly?</i>
<i>- There's even an address.</i>

27
00:01:34,041 --> 00:01:36,208
<i>- She doesn't look like a murderer.</i>
<i>- Someone post a photo.</i>

28
00:01:36,291 --> 00:01:38,250
YEH PIN-HSUAN - ABOUT

29
00:01:38,333 --> 00:01:40,000
PRE-ORDER PHONE NUMBER - COPY

30
00:01:40,083 --> 00:01:41,750
LANE 46, BINGJIANG STREET, WANHUA DISTRICT

31
00:01:41,833 --> 00:01:44,250
<i>Let's confront her directly.</i>

32
00:01:44,333 --> 00:01:46,000
<i>- They found her.</i>
<i>- We should all show up together.</i>

33
00:01:46,083 --> 00:01:48,125
- <i>There's an address.</i>
- <i>The police know about it.</i>

34
00:01:48,208 --> 00:01:49,500
<i>Dox her!</i>

35
00:03:04,791 --> 00:03:06,041
<i>I think it's this one over here.</i>

36
00:03:06,125 --> 00:03:07,333
<i>- Yeah, this one here.</i>
<i>- This one?</i>

37
00:03:07,416 --> 00:03:08,458
<i>Yeah. Number 48.</i>

38
00:03:08,541 --> 00:03:10,125
<i>- Get your ass out here.</i>
<i>- Yeah, fuck you.</i>

39
00:03:10,208 --> 00:03:11,833
<i>- We just wanna talk.</i>
<i>- Add some ingredients.</i>

40
00:03:11,916 --> 00:03:13,166
<i>- Yeah.</i>
<i>- Get it all on there.</i>

41
00:03:13,250 --> 00:03:15,541
<i>- Bitch. You deserve this.</i>
<i>- What are you gonna do, huh?!</i>

42
00:03:15,625 --> 00:03:17,333
<i>Add the strawberry sauce.</i>

43
00:03:17,416 --> 00:03:18,416
<i>Come on! </i>

44
00:03:18,500 --> 00:03:20,250
<i>- Fuck. Someone's coming.</i>
<i>- Let's get out of here! Run!</i>

45
00:03:20,333 --> 00:03:21,333
<i>Go, go!</i>

46
00:03:48,416 --> 00:03:50,208
WHAT TO DO ON SATURDAY

47
00:03:50,291 --> 00:03:51,500
A CREAM CAKE FOR YOU ON SATURDAY!

48
00:03:53,083 --> 00:03:54,541
<i>Hey. Get a look at this guy.</i>

49
00:03:54,625 --> 00:03:56,375
<i>Hey. Hey, you.</i>

50
00:03:56,458 --> 00:03:58,541
<i>Happy birthday! </i>

51
00:03:58,625 --> 00:04:01,708
<i>Happy birthday to you!</i>
<i>Happy birthday to you! </i>

52
00:04:01,791 --> 00:04:04,625
<i>Hey, aren't you gonna</i>
<i>blow out the candle and--</i>

53
00:04:08,208 --> 00:04:10,583
<i>Happy birthday to-- </i>

54
00:04:19,833 --> 00:04:20,833
LIN X YU

55
00:04:38,291 --> 00:04:39,500
Hello?

56
00:04:39,583 --> 00:04:41,583
Yo Tzu. How are you feeling?

57
00:04:43,791 --> 00:04:45,833
Still alive.

58
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:49,708
Hey. I saw Yeh Pin-hsuan in a TikTok.

59
00:04:49,791 --> 00:04:51,750
- <i>So?</i>
- Just sent it.

60
00:04:53,708 --> 00:04:55,833
<i>It's one of Lin Po-lun's videos.</i>

61
00:04:55,916 --> 00:04:58,458
<i>I ordered cake from Sweet Spot</i>
<i>a few days ago,</i>

62
00:04:58,541 --> 00:05:01,083
<i>and the one who delivered it</i>
<i>was Lin Po-lun.</i>

63
00:05:01,166 --> 00:05:04,041
And? So what?

64
00:05:04,125 --> 00:05:05,708
Don't you get it?

65
00:05:05,791 --> 00:05:08,875
Yeh Pin-hsuan appeared
in Lin Po-lun's channel.

66
00:05:08,958 --> 00:05:13,750
Lin Po-lun then delivered cake for her.
They must be connected somehow.

67
00:05:13,833 --> 00:05:15,708
Maybe they were a couple?

68
00:05:15,791 --> 00:05:19,625
So, a psychotic couple killed each other?

69
00:05:20,125 --> 00:05:22,333
What does that have to do with me?

70
00:05:22,416 --> 00:05:24,333
<i>Don't you think that's strange?</i>

71
00:05:25,708 --> 00:05:27,958
What's strange about it?

72
00:05:28,041 --> 00:05:29,833
That would mean the killer…

73
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:39,916
This was an impulsive killing.

74
00:05:41,333 --> 00:05:46,166
We suspect she killed Lin Po-lun.
But presently, we don't have a motive.

75
00:05:47,541 --> 00:05:50,791
But we're sure
that Wa Zai's killer was male.

76
00:05:50,875 --> 00:05:54,583
But she was present at both crime scenes.

77
00:05:54,666 --> 00:05:57,041
And in RS Esports.

78
00:05:57,125 --> 00:05:58,791
- Oh, fuck.
- What do we do?

79
00:05:58,875 --> 00:06:00,333
Should we help?

80
00:06:08,166 --> 00:06:09,791
It's not random.

81
00:06:10,375 --> 00:06:12,291
<i>What? What did you say?</i>

82
00:06:14,833 --> 00:06:17,000
KAO PI - AUDIO CALL

83
00:07:07,083 --> 00:07:10,416
AMY HOSTEL CALLING

84
00:07:55,875 --> 00:07:56,875
399.

85
00:07:56,958 --> 00:07:58,291
Thank you.

86
00:07:58,375 --> 00:08:00,291
And… here's your change.

87
00:08:12,208 --> 00:08:13,875
Where did you go just now?

88
00:08:14,375 --> 00:08:16,000
I just went shopping.

89
00:08:16,958 --> 00:08:18,166
What did you buy?

90
00:08:18,250 --> 00:08:19,500
I'll show you when we get home.

91
00:08:19,583 --> 00:08:22,000
- What did you buy? Let me see.
- I'll show you when we get home!

92
00:08:22,083 --> 00:08:23,583
- Just go home first! Stop!
- Show me.

93
00:08:28,916 --> 00:08:30,750
Do you wanna kill me?

94
00:08:30,833 --> 00:08:32,958
- No. I… Let's just go home, okay?
- Huh?

95
00:08:33,041 --> 00:08:34,125
- Come here.
- Stop!

96
00:08:40,041 --> 00:08:42,958
I'm sorry! I'm sorry.
Please, stop. Please.

97
00:09:11,458 --> 00:09:12,458
You…

98
00:09:43,333 --> 00:09:45,375
AMY HOSTEL CALLING

99
00:09:47,916 --> 00:09:51,541
Close all footbridges in Taipei now!
And find Yeh Pin-hsuan!

100
00:09:51,625 --> 00:09:54,916
But, Captain, Taipei
has got 79 footbridges. Where--

101
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:57,625
You talk to the precincts
to get extra support!

102
00:09:58,208 --> 00:09:59,208
Let's get on it.

103
00:09:59,291 --> 00:10:02,041
Retrieve all surveillance footage
around footbridges.

104
00:10:02,125 --> 00:10:04,333
What? Another dead body?

105
00:10:05,541 --> 00:10:07,125
Near the Keelung Road intersection.

106
00:10:07,208 --> 00:10:08,333
Let's go.

107
00:10:08,416 --> 00:10:10,083
Move. Quickly. Go. Go now.

108
00:10:10,166 --> 00:10:11,875
Let's go, everyone.

109
00:10:14,250 --> 00:10:15,625
Go now. Hurry.

110
00:10:15,708 --> 00:10:17,625
- Hsin-ping, move faster.
- Sir.

111
00:10:21,625 --> 00:10:23,375
- Li Hsin-ping…
- Sir.

112
00:10:23,458 --> 00:10:24,625
You stay here.

113
00:10:47,291 --> 00:10:49,666
They must have really pissed someone off.

114
00:10:50,208 --> 00:10:52,500
Has anyone called the police?
Have they come yet?

115
00:10:55,041 --> 00:10:57,625
- Really? They did that?
- Pardon me. Sorry.

116
00:10:58,208 --> 00:11:02,000
Who does this?
Orphans. No one would cry if they die.

117
00:11:02,083 --> 00:11:03,875
I can't believe they did this. For what?

118
00:11:03,958 --> 00:11:06,208
Excuse me. Do you know
the person who lives here?

119
00:11:06,291 --> 00:11:08,250
Of course I do. I own this place.

120
00:11:08,333 --> 00:11:11,000
They see something on the news
and take it upon themselves to do this.

121
00:11:11,083 --> 00:11:12,708
Please open the door. I'm with the police.

122
00:11:12,791 --> 00:11:14,625
Oh. The police are involved?

123
00:11:14,708 --> 00:11:17,083
Even the police are here.
This time, it's serious, I guess.

124
00:11:35,458 --> 00:11:39,125
FREELANCER CLASS APPOINTMENT
FLOUR, RAW MILK, CAKE BOX FACTORY

125
00:11:55,250 --> 00:11:57,083
Aah! Aah…

126
00:13:03,333 --> 00:13:04,708
- Calm down.
- Kao Pi!

127
00:13:04,791 --> 00:13:06,791
Hey.

128
00:13:07,583 --> 00:13:08,916
Calm down.

129
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,750
Kao Pi!

130
00:13:49,708 --> 00:13:52,666
Less than ten minutes
after Witch Baba posted this video,

131
00:13:52,750 --> 00:13:54,791
the fifth victim was discovered.

132
00:13:54,875 --> 00:13:57,625
Police have already revealed
the victim's identity.

133
00:13:57,708 --> 00:14:00,250
A famous influencer named Kao Pi.

134
00:14:00,333 --> 00:14:01,875
This video is now going viral,

135
00:14:01,958 --> 00:14:05,666
with the popular theory being
that Witch Baba is a copycat killer

136
00:14:05,750 --> 00:14:07,666
and the real killer is still at large.

137
00:14:07,750 --> 00:14:11,500
In other breaking news, the police
have discovered the body of Yeh Pin-hsuan

138
00:14:11,583 --> 00:14:14,541
who committed suicide
at her home early this morning.

139
00:14:17,125 --> 00:14:18,708
Yes, sir. I know.

140
00:14:23,458 --> 00:14:24,958
I got it. Okay.

141
00:14:26,125 --> 00:14:27,916
I'll do my best to handle it.

142
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,166
Okay. Got it.

143
00:14:29,250 --> 00:14:30,333
Thanks, sir.

144
00:14:33,166 --> 00:14:34,291
Sir.

145
00:14:36,541 --> 00:14:39,916
The case is being taken over
by the High Technology Unit.

146
00:14:40,583 --> 00:14:44,583
It's now a serial murder case.
The division head's involved.

147
00:14:44,666 --> 00:14:47,791
Full authority goes to the
High Technology Crime Investigation Unit.

148
00:14:47,875 --> 00:14:48,750
Yes, sir.

149
00:14:50,583 --> 00:14:53,416
It won't involve you.
What are you doing, now?

150
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:56,208
I'm informing colleagues
about the situation.

151
00:14:56,291 --> 00:14:58,125
How many more do you wanna kill?

152
00:14:58,833 --> 00:14:59,666
Huh?

153
00:14:59,750 --> 00:15:01,333
Did you leak information
about Yeh Pin-hsuan?

154
00:15:03,250 --> 00:15:04,083
Huh?

155
00:15:05,166 --> 00:15:07,458
Her being doxed online was your fault.

156
00:15:07,541 --> 00:15:09,583
Her brand was boycotted!

157
00:15:09,666 --> 00:15:11,666
You caused her online bullying.

158
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:13,416
You caused Yeh Pin-hsuan's death!

159
00:15:14,166 --> 00:15:15,000
Sir.

160
00:15:15,083 --> 00:15:17,000
The heads are gonna come down hard.

161
00:15:17,083 --> 00:15:19,291
Chances are I'm done for
and Mr. Jen's done for!

162
00:15:19,375 --> 00:15:20,708
I want you out of this unit.

163
00:15:20,791 --> 00:15:23,333
Until it's finalized,
you're off active duty.

164
00:15:23,416 --> 00:15:24,458
But, sir…

165
00:15:25,458 --> 00:15:28,458
- It's not her fault, sir.
- I know. It's your doing!

166
00:15:34,166 --> 00:15:37,000
Your video is on the internet!

167
00:15:52,708 --> 00:15:54,333
IS IT FUN TO BLOW UP A CAR WITH FIREWORKS?

168
00:15:54,416 --> 00:15:55,416
THE TRUTH IS OUT!

169
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:57,125
WEI YEN, WA ZAI, KAO PI, YO TZU!

170
00:15:57,208 --> 00:15:59,000
THE KILLER WANTS TO TAKE REVENGE ON THEM

171
00:15:59,083 --> 00:16:01,208
WITCH BABA IS TARGETING THEM
FROM THE START

172
00:16:01,291 --> 00:16:02,541
YO TZU, WANNA EXPLAIN THIS?

173
00:16:02,625 --> 00:16:03,916
YO TZU, COME OUT AND FACE THIS

174
00:16:05,250 --> 00:16:07,250
Witch Baba's been targeting you
from the start,

175
00:16:07,333 --> 00:16:08,625
and you didn't tell us this?

176
00:16:12,708 --> 00:16:15,166
No way. It's not related to this.

177
00:16:15,250 --> 00:16:18,041
How long have you hidden this
from everyone?

178
00:16:18,625 --> 00:16:20,625
I didn't hide it. Uh… I…

179
00:16:31,250 --> 00:16:35,250
You're a person of interest now.
You be sure to cooperate.

180
00:16:37,916 --> 00:16:39,708
Take him back to the hospital.

181
00:16:59,541 --> 00:17:00,541
Hey.

182
00:17:04,250 --> 00:17:06,166
Are you okay?

183
00:17:12,333 --> 00:17:13,458
You okay?

184
00:17:16,083 --> 00:17:18,000
What do you mean by that?

185
00:17:18,083 --> 00:17:19,416
How can you still smile?

186
00:17:25,333 --> 00:17:28,625
You guys acting like idiots
has caused all this to happen.

187
00:17:28,708 --> 00:17:32,458
How was I meant to know
it would turn out like this?

188
00:17:32,541 --> 00:17:35,500
- Did anyone get hurt or die?
- Of course not.

189
00:17:35,583 --> 00:17:37,166
Oh, really?

190
00:17:38,833 --> 00:17:39,916
I don't know.

191
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:44,708
It all seemed so fine back then.

192
00:17:44,791 --> 00:17:46,083
Seemed?

193
00:17:47,833 --> 00:17:50,625
It was very serious.
Why didn't you call an ambulance?

194
00:17:50,708 --> 00:17:52,250
Why didn't you tell this to Mr. Jen?

195
00:17:52,333 --> 00:17:53,833
How was I to know it was related?

196
00:17:53,916 --> 00:17:54,958
Of course it is.

197
00:17:55,541 --> 00:17:59,333
If you'd told the police earlier,
we could've cracked this case by now.

198
00:17:59,416 --> 00:18:03,333
Kao Pi died because of you.
Wa Zai and Yeh Pin-hsuan too.

199
00:18:11,041 --> 00:18:12,166
Hey.

200
00:18:12,250 --> 00:18:15,208
Hey. Wait. Why does it affect you so much?

201
00:18:15,291 --> 00:18:17,041
She didn't die because of you.

202
00:18:19,541 --> 00:18:21,541
Others, they died because of me.

203
00:18:22,208 --> 00:18:24,708
They? Who's they?

204
00:18:26,166 --> 00:18:27,375
Not your concern.

205
00:18:27,458 --> 00:18:28,458
Wait.

206
00:18:29,583 --> 00:18:30,791
Look.

207
00:18:32,041 --> 00:18:35,791
I've already gone viral online.
I need to know.

208
00:18:35,875 --> 00:18:37,875
I could be next.

209
00:18:45,125 --> 00:18:48,500
My friend has gone missing.
It's already been five days now.

210
00:18:48,583 --> 00:18:50,083
Please find her.

211
00:18:51,250 --> 00:18:54,208
<i>We don't have</i>
<i>a search warrant. Do you wanna get sued?</i>

212
00:18:56,833 --> 00:18:59,000
<i>We could apply for a search warrant.</i>

213
00:18:59,083 --> 00:19:02,208
<i>Go and request it yourself</i>
<i>if you think it's that easy.</i>

214
00:19:03,541 --> 00:19:06,500
- Sir? I want a search warrant.
- Here we go again.

215
00:19:07,083 --> 00:19:09,708
I suspect his girlfriend's in the house.

216
00:19:09,791 --> 00:19:12,875
Didn't you go there?
Did you see a girlfriend?

217
00:19:13,583 --> 00:19:15,125
I couldn't see his girlfriend

218
00:19:15,208 --> 00:19:17,333
because I didn't have
a search warrant, did I?

219
00:19:17,416 --> 00:19:18,583
When we were at the door,

220
00:19:18,666 --> 00:19:20,833
his dog kept barking
at the door of another room, and I--

221
00:19:20,916 --> 00:19:22,750
So the dog was barking.

222
00:19:23,708 --> 00:19:24,958
CASE REPORTING PROCEDURE

223
00:19:25,041 --> 00:19:26,041
You know the procedure.

224
00:19:36,041 --> 00:19:37,250
CHEN WEI-JOU

225
00:19:46,083 --> 00:19:48,083
CHEN CHEN: WHAT? WHAT HAPPENED?

226
00:19:50,166 --> 00:19:52,458
SINGLE

227
00:19:58,333 --> 00:20:00,041
Mister, this is a search warrant

228
00:20:00,125 --> 00:20:03,708
from the Taipei City District Court.
Open the door now.

229
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:09,291
Hey! Stop. Stop!

230
00:20:10,333 --> 00:20:12,041
Put your hands behind your back!

231
00:20:25,875 --> 00:20:27,458
Get off! Get off me!

232
00:20:32,041 --> 00:20:33,416
<i>I only found out later on</i>

233
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:36,416
<i>that her boyfriend</i>
<i>wouldn't agree to a breakup,</i>

234
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:38,083
<i>so he locked her up.</i>

235
00:20:40,208 --> 00:20:43,458
<i>Turns out</i>
<i>she'd been a prisoner for two weeks.</i>

236
00:20:44,458 --> 00:20:47,041
<i>In the end, she chose to die.</i>

237
00:20:50,083 --> 00:20:54,375
<i>I've always wondered,</i>
<i>if I had gone in a bit sooner,</i>

238
00:20:56,500 --> 00:21:00,291
<i>would she still… be alive today?</i>

239
00:21:00,375 --> 00:21:01,458
POLICE SCIENCE

240
00:21:01,541 --> 00:21:05,083
<i>That was when I decided</i>
<i>to get into the Crime Investigation Unit.</i>

241
00:21:06,583 --> 00:21:09,250
<i>I wanted to be able</i>
<i>to help these people on the edge</i>

242
00:21:09,333 --> 00:21:12,291
<i>in a more efficient and speedy way.</i>

243
00:21:16,458 --> 00:21:18,375
Even now, I still think…

244
00:21:20,541 --> 00:21:21,875
I'm useless.

245
00:21:23,375 --> 00:21:27,166
Be it the past or present,
despite which unit I'm in.

246
00:21:29,958 --> 00:21:31,750
I can't change anything.

247
00:21:45,375 --> 00:21:46,791
Why are you following me?

248
00:21:46,875 --> 00:21:50,125
Your boss told you
to take me back to hospital.

249
00:21:50,208 --> 00:21:51,583
Then take a cab.

250
00:21:52,291 --> 00:21:53,291
Wait. I…

251
00:21:54,541 --> 00:21:57,208
Hey! I'm injured!

252
00:21:57,291 --> 00:21:59,708
What exactly do you want from me?

253
00:21:59,791 --> 00:22:02,166
You're good at your job.

254
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:05,375
Because you help people who need it.

255
00:22:06,416 --> 00:22:08,833
- I told you, I'm useless.
- I need your help.

256
00:22:11,208 --> 00:22:13,708
Witch Baba is involved in this.

257
00:22:14,208 --> 00:22:18,375
If I don't find out how,
I'll live in trauma forever.

258
00:22:19,625 --> 00:22:20,958
It will haunt me.

259
00:22:21,041 --> 00:22:22,541
What do I care?

260
00:22:22,625 --> 00:22:25,250
Hey. You wanted to be a cop.

261
00:22:26,250 --> 00:22:28,750
There must've been a reason for it.
Something deep down.

262
00:22:34,250 --> 00:22:35,250
Help me?

263
00:22:48,083 --> 00:22:51,250
I wanted to become an influencer
to get my dad's attention.

264
00:22:51,333 --> 00:22:54,083
When I was young, he had gambling debts.

265
00:22:54,166 --> 00:22:56,958
So he left home. I rarely saw him.

266
00:22:57,625 --> 00:22:59,166
He said he'd visit.

267
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:01,416
It's all bullshit.

268
00:23:02,958 --> 00:23:05,791
So I worked hard
to become a popular influencer

269
00:23:05,875 --> 00:23:07,291
and acted a fool,

270
00:23:08,416 --> 00:23:12,250
hoping that he'd see me online
and remember I exist.

271
00:23:13,500 --> 00:23:15,708
But when I got to 500K subs,

272
00:23:15,791 --> 00:23:20,458
I found out that…
he had already died years ago.

273
00:23:22,291 --> 00:23:23,666
I was depressed.

274
00:23:24,375 --> 00:23:29,333
But then a follower
told me that when her mom died,

275
00:23:29,416 --> 00:23:31,583
my videos helped her get through it.

276
00:23:32,208 --> 00:23:34,125
My videos helped her.

277
00:23:37,041 --> 00:23:38,791
I don't know how we got here.

278
00:23:41,083 --> 00:23:44,041
But I think
this is something only we can do.

279
00:23:46,333 --> 00:23:48,208
We haven't caught the killer yet.

280
00:23:48,875 --> 00:23:50,250
So snap out of it.

281
00:23:57,791 --> 00:23:59,291
It's not that easy.

282
00:24:04,000 --> 00:24:06,458
Yeh Pin-hsuan was Witch Baba's copycat.

283
00:24:08,458 --> 00:24:12,125
Maybe that means
that Witch Baba contacted her.

284
00:24:12,833 --> 00:24:14,750
She did contact Wa Zai.

285
00:24:18,583 --> 00:24:19,708
Wait up.

286
00:24:20,583 --> 00:24:23,333
Chen Chia-jen knew all this.
Didn't he tell you?

287
00:24:26,250 --> 00:24:28,041
They don't tell me anything.

288
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:30,000
Hey.

289
00:24:30,083 --> 00:24:31,083
Wait.

290
00:24:33,291 --> 00:24:34,833
Where are you going now?

291
00:24:34,916 --> 00:24:36,208
Back to my unit.

292
00:24:36,291 --> 00:24:37,833
You're gonna go back?

293
00:24:38,500 --> 00:24:41,541
I wanted this job
so I could make a difference.

294
00:25:05,083 --> 00:25:08,083
OPEN

295
00:26:11,416 --> 00:26:12,708
Um…

296
00:26:12,791 --> 00:26:14,958
- Can I help you?
- I'd like to know…

297
00:26:15,625 --> 00:26:17,791
- What is it?
- Do you sell these here?

298
00:26:19,916 --> 00:26:23,458
Ah. Those are very popular.
I'm out of stock now.

299
00:26:23,541 --> 00:26:25,333
- That so?
- You can't find those anywhere.

300
00:26:25,416 --> 00:26:27,833
- Also, this one here.
- Hey…

301
00:26:29,666 --> 00:26:31,083
This girl here…

302
00:26:32,083 --> 00:26:33,541
Do you know her?

303
00:26:35,083 --> 00:26:38,458
<i>Do I know her? She comes here often.</i>

304
00:26:38,541 --> 00:26:40,041
<i>What did she buy?</i>

305
00:26:40,125 --> 00:26:42,125
<i>The cards you are looking for.</i>

306
00:26:43,291 --> 00:26:44,666
<i>And a mask.</i>

307
00:27:03,208 --> 00:27:04,583
Yu-chieh.

308
00:27:34,375 --> 00:27:35,416
Yu-chieh?

309
00:27:42,708 --> 00:27:44,750
Yu-chieh?

310
00:27:44,833 --> 00:27:46,750
<i>Guess what I got on my test.</i>

311
00:27:53,958 --> 00:27:56,875
You're home. Let's eat.

312
00:30:56,708 --> 00:31:00,791
Without access to Pin-hsuan's phone,
we'll have to rely on ourselves.

313
00:31:01,416 --> 00:31:02,916
What's the plan?

314
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:04,750
Hop on and we'll talk about it.

315
00:31:11,208 --> 00:31:12,333
- Hey…
- Set?

316
00:31:12,416 --> 00:31:17,458
Is it possible
to restore deleted phone videos?

317
00:31:18,583 --> 00:31:19,833
That's easy.

318
00:31:25,458 --> 00:31:26,958
EVIDENCE ROOM

319
00:31:35,833 --> 00:31:37,000
Hi. Working hard.

320
00:31:37,083 --> 00:31:38,875
OFFICER ON DUTY
SHEN WEI-HAO

321
00:31:38,958 --> 00:31:41,000
- What do you got there?
- Evidence.

322
00:31:41,083 --> 00:31:43,125
What? From what case?

323
00:31:43,208 --> 00:31:45,708
I just shut down
an illegal balloon vendor.

324
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:49,625
Yeah, but why are you the one
who seized it?

325
00:31:49,708 --> 00:31:51,166
Goes with the job.

326
00:31:51,875 --> 00:31:53,625
Ohh!

327
00:31:53,708 --> 00:31:56,458
Ahh! Oh boy. I'm such a klutz.

328
00:31:56,541 --> 00:31:59,875
That was too heavy. You think
you could help me carry these upstairs?

329
00:31:59,958 --> 00:32:01,750
Can't you see I'm on duty right now?

330
00:32:01,833 --> 00:32:03,750
Yeah, I know. When you get a chance.

331
00:32:03,833 --> 00:32:05,541
- Hey.
- Thanks! I owe you one.

332
00:32:05,625 --> 00:32:07,000
Come back!

333
00:32:11,666 --> 00:32:13,791
So annoying.

334
00:32:32,250 --> 00:32:34,458
You're meant to be at the hospital.

335
00:32:34,541 --> 00:32:35,875
Oh. Uh…

336
00:32:35,958 --> 00:32:39,250
Uh… I came to return… Officer Li's keys.

337
00:32:40,750 --> 00:32:41,583
Give it to me.

338
00:32:41,666 --> 00:32:42,875
It's okay.
I'll just put it in the cabinet.

339
00:32:42,958 --> 00:32:44,041
Give it to me.

340
00:32:56,500 --> 00:32:58,541
These are her keys?

341
00:32:59,333 --> 00:33:01,750
Pretty crazy.

342
00:33:01,833 --> 00:33:05,083
- Hey. Didn't I tell you to call me first?
- I don't have your phone number.

343
00:33:05,166 --> 00:33:06,416
Well, you should've called.

344
00:33:06,500 --> 00:33:07,958
- What? How?
- How are you?

345
00:33:09,541 --> 00:33:11,125
These are your keys?

346
00:33:14,083 --> 00:33:15,875
Yes. These are mine.

347
00:33:19,708 --> 00:33:22,666
- Aren't you leaving?
- Thanks for your service.

348
00:33:22,750 --> 00:33:25,416
Oh. What are all my balloons doing here?

349
00:33:25,500 --> 00:33:27,875
Hey, thanks. Thanks for my keys. Bye.

350
00:33:29,666 --> 00:33:30,791
Oh. Mr. Li.

351
00:35:42,500 --> 00:35:43,666
What are you up to?

352
00:35:43,750 --> 00:35:45,000
Sir.

353
00:35:47,541 --> 00:35:48,791
You stealing evidence?

354
00:35:49,375 --> 00:35:51,583
No. I was submitting evidence.

355
00:35:52,541 --> 00:35:54,958
Then why are you hiding
behind the cabinet?

356
00:35:55,041 --> 00:35:58,291
Uh… This fell down.
I was down there grabbing it.

357
00:35:59,583 --> 00:36:00,583
What is it?

358
00:36:02,333 --> 00:36:04,000
I don't know.

359
00:36:04,083 --> 00:36:05,250
Hand it over.

360
00:36:12,083 --> 00:36:14,208
What exactly are you doing in here?!

361
00:36:14,916 --> 00:36:16,708
I came to submit evidence.

362
00:36:18,583 --> 00:36:20,208
You're sneaking around.

363
00:36:20,291 --> 00:36:21,291
Get out.

364
00:36:21,833 --> 00:36:22,916
Yes, sir.

365
00:36:24,791 --> 00:36:25,833
Li Hsin-ping.

366
00:36:30,833 --> 00:36:32,875
Don't forget. You're part of this unit.

367
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:35,083
Of course.

368
00:36:49,833 --> 00:36:52,000
Hey. Yo Tzu.

369
00:36:52,083 --> 00:36:54,500
Catch. Here.

370
00:37:08,583 --> 00:37:09,958
Ah, shit.

371
00:37:10,041 --> 00:37:11,041
Hey.

372
00:37:11,791 --> 00:37:13,541
- Give it to me.
- What the…

373
00:37:14,250 --> 00:37:15,708
The phone's locked.

374
00:37:16,250 --> 00:37:18,500
Shouldn't be a problem. Here.

375
00:37:21,625 --> 00:37:22,625
What's that?

376
00:37:22,708 --> 00:37:24,458
It's a decoder.

377
00:37:25,916 --> 00:37:28,083
Oh, shit.

378
00:38:33,250 --> 00:38:35,958
She deleted her Facebook. And IG.

379
00:38:38,666 --> 00:38:41,166
Well, that's because she was targeted.

380
00:38:41,250 --> 00:38:42,916
Let's see what's in her call history.

381
00:38:58,875 --> 00:39:01,375
BIG FIRE IN WULAI
FOOD SAFETY BREACH - FATAL CAR ACCIDENT

382
00:39:18,208 --> 00:39:21,750
BULGARIAN TEXT DETECTED
DO YOU WANT TO AUTOMATICALLY TRANSLATE IT?

383
00:39:25,208 --> 00:39:28,208
CALLING

384
00:39:28,291 --> 00:39:29,916
SPEAKER

385
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:31,666
<i>Welcome to Amy Hostel.</i>

386
00:39:31,750 --> 00:39:33,541
<i>For Chinese service, please press 1.</i>

387
00:39:33,625 --> 00:39:36,708
- Hostel? Why did she call there?
<i>- For English service, please press 2.</i>

388
00:39:36,791 --> 00:39:40,125
BULGARIAN - CHINESE (TRADITIONAL)

389
00:39:45,791 --> 00:39:47,333
<i>Amy Hostel.</i>

390
00:40:20,333 --> 00:40:21,416
Hello.

391
00:40:21,500 --> 00:40:24,833
I'm a police officer.
I'd like to see your guest register.

392
00:40:24,916 --> 00:40:27,000
Oh, okay. Let me get the manager.

393
00:40:27,083 --> 00:40:28,500
Okay. Please hurry.

394
00:40:30,250 --> 00:40:34,750
Hello, sir. There's a police officer here
that wants to see the guest list.

395
00:40:36,458 --> 00:40:38,125
Oh-- Yes.

396
00:40:50,416 --> 00:40:51,708
Witch Baba?

397
00:40:55,666 --> 00:40:56,916
It's actually her.

398
00:40:57,000 --> 00:40:58,000
Hey!

399
00:41:04,625 --> 00:41:08,083
- Hey! Stop!
- I can't run that fast. Hey!

400
00:41:09,208 --> 00:41:10,666
Hey!

401
00:41:17,458 --> 00:41:19,125
Go around the other side!

402
00:41:21,416 --> 00:41:22,875
Where's the other side?

403
00:41:37,875 --> 00:41:39,375
Stop where you are!

404
00:41:45,041 --> 00:41:46,708
- Stop running!
- No!

405
00:41:49,166 --> 00:41:51,791
- Stop running.
- Stop running!

406
00:41:51,875 --> 00:41:52,958
Who are you?

407
00:41:53,625 --> 00:41:54,625
Tell me your name.

408
00:41:58,250 --> 00:41:59,916
Where is my daughter?

409
00:42:00,583 --> 00:42:01,833
Tell me where my daughter is.

410
00:42:01,916 --> 00:42:03,416
I don't know. I don't know.

411
00:42:03,500 --> 00:42:05,458
I wanna know
where my daughter is! Tell me now!

412
00:42:05,541 --> 00:42:07,958
I don't know. I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

413
00:42:09,583 --> 00:42:10,666
Where is she?

414
00:42:12,416 --> 00:42:14,541
I'm asking you. Where is Yu-chieh?

415
00:42:19,875 --> 00:42:21,458
Please save Yu-chieh!

416
00:42:22,958 --> 00:42:24,791
Save Yu-chieh, okay?

417
00:42:24,875 --> 00:42:27,666
Please! Please save her!

418
00:42:28,750 --> 00:42:32,500
Please save her!

419
00:42:47,916 --> 00:42:49,625
We're doing this one, right?

420
00:42:51,375 --> 00:42:52,750
Don't forget the candle.

421
00:42:53,875 --> 00:42:55,041
Oh, yeah.

422
00:42:57,958 --> 00:42:59,125
Thanks.

423
00:43:09,416 --> 00:43:12,208
- Hey. Don't be nervous.
- I'm not.

424
00:43:12,291 --> 00:43:14,000
You look so stiff.

425
00:43:14,500 --> 00:43:15,875
- I'm good.
- Ready?

426
00:43:19,958 --> 00:43:22,333
Don't be nervous.
We can get multiple takes.

427
00:43:22,416 --> 00:43:23,833
I'm feeling good.

428
00:43:25,583 --> 00:43:27,666
Ready… Action.

429
00:43:27,750 --> 00:43:29,375
Hello. I'm Witch Baba.

430
00:43:29,458 --> 00:43:31,291
Today is February 15.

431
00:43:31,375 --> 00:43:33,833
The fire I predicted last time
really happened.

432
00:43:33,916 --> 00:43:36,041
Everyone must be careful
when using a heater--

433
00:43:36,125 --> 00:43:36,958
Hang on!

434
00:43:37,541 --> 00:43:38,791
- What?
- You forgot your mask.

435
00:43:38,875 --> 00:43:40,958
Oh! I completely forgot.

436
00:43:41,041 --> 00:43:43,250
- Put it on. Here. I'll help you.
- Okay.

437
00:43:43,333 --> 00:43:44,166
Thanks.

438
00:43:44,250 --> 00:43:45,541
- Ow!
- What?

439
00:43:45,625 --> 00:43:48,000
Wait, it hurts. You pulled the back.

440
00:43:48,083 --> 00:43:50,125
- I didn't. Here. You do it.
- Yeah. You did!

441
00:43:50,208 --> 00:43:51,791
- What do you mean? Huh?
- Here. You try it.

442
00:43:51,875 --> 00:43:53,416
- What are you on about?
- Here. Try it on.

443
00:43:53,500 --> 00:43:56,000
- You're the one talking.
- Here. Just try it.

444
00:43:56,083 --> 00:43:58,208
- Why would I wear it?
- Just feel it.

445
00:44:02,458 --> 00:44:07,000
So, someone kidnapped your friend
and forced you to make predictions.

446
00:44:10,041 --> 00:44:13,458
So you did it?
Why didn't you call the police?

447
00:44:13,541 --> 00:44:15,583
I didn't know people would die.

448
00:44:16,083 --> 00:44:18,000
And I don't know who he actually is.

449
00:44:18,083 --> 00:44:19,291
- Or if he would hurt her.
- Fuck!

450
00:44:19,375 --> 00:44:22,833
So you've been in contact with him
for so long and you don't know who he is?

451
00:44:22,916 --> 00:44:25,250
Do you know who he really is?

452
00:44:25,333 --> 00:44:27,500
I'm not the one who caused the accident.

453
00:44:30,666 --> 00:44:33,958
So, then, why did he go to you?

454
00:44:35,250 --> 00:44:37,250
Why did he choose you of all people?

455
00:44:38,625 --> 00:44:41,625
And why did you upload videos
from an internet café?

456
00:44:41,708 --> 00:44:44,875
- Is that how he found you?
- I really don't know.

457
00:44:45,958 --> 00:44:47,583
Why are you acting like a victim?

458
00:44:47,666 --> 00:44:49,583
Why did you call Yeh Pin-hsuan?

459
00:44:52,583 --> 00:44:54,875
Originally, I thought it was her.

460
00:44:54,958 --> 00:44:57,583
I just wanted
to ask her not to kill people.

461
00:45:05,875 --> 00:45:07,500
What about the car accident?

462
00:45:08,625 --> 00:45:10,291
Why do you have that video?

463
00:45:14,875 --> 00:45:19,625
If it really was because of the accident,
I think I might know why.

464
00:45:23,250 --> 00:45:25,791
<i>Witch Baba's predictions are all fake.</i>

465
00:45:25,875 --> 00:45:29,708
<i>But a year ago,</i>
<i>Witch Baba predicted a car accident.</i>

466
00:45:31,166 --> 00:45:33,541
<i>Upright Intercontinental Missile.</i>

467
00:45:34,500 --> 00:45:36,833
<i>Reversed Statue of Liberty.</i>

468
00:45:36,916 --> 00:45:39,583
<i>Upright The Great Fire of London.</i>

469
00:45:40,458 --> 00:45:43,125
<i>Next, there will be a car accident!</i>

470
00:45:44,541 --> 00:45:47,000
<i>It was the car accident in your video.</i>

471
00:45:52,791 --> 00:45:56,750
NEIHU FATAL CAR ACCIDENT
MOM AND DAUGHTER BOTH DIED
